column1: 1|"room00"|"You are in a jungle with a beach to one side of you. There is a cave ahead in the distance."
2|"room01"|"You are standing on a beach, feeling the hot sand beneath your feet. You can see a jungle in one direction, a forest in another, and a stone temple straight ahead."
3|"room02"|"You are in a dense forest with trees surrounding you. You cannot see any other areas through the thick foliage."
4|"room10"|"You are inside a dark cave. It is very difficult to see anything."
